usage :
	tetris a [level]
		Classic "survival" mode
	tetris b [level] [high]
		25 line to complete, with a handicap
	tetris 2 :[port] [level [high]]
		Launches the server for a 2 player mode listening on the port port
	tetris 2 ip:[port] [level [high]]
		Connects to a given server for a 2 player game

	level has an influence on the speed of piece dropping and must be in [0,9]
	high must be in [0,5] and a non zero value adds random blocks at the bottom of the grid


	Default values are :
		level : 0
		high : 0
		port : 37280

